| Column Name             | Data Type         | Category                    | Description                                                                          |
| ----------------------- | ----------------- | --------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| `Patient_ID`            | Object (String)   | Categorical                 | Unique identification number assigned to each cancer patient.                        |
| `Age`                   | Integer (`int64`) | Numerical                   | Age of the patient in years.                                                         |
| `Gender`                | Object (String)   | Categorical                 | Gender of the patient such as Male, Female, or Other.                                |
| `Country_Region`        | Object (String)   | Categorical                 | Country or region where the patient belongs.                                         |
| `Year`                  | Integer (`int64`) | Numerical                   | Year in which the patient record was captured (2015–2024).                           |
| `Genetic_Risk`          | Float (`float64`) | Numerical                   | Genetic predisposition score indicating inherited cancer risk level.                 |
| `Air_Pollution`         | Float (`float64`) | Numerical                   | Air pollution exposure score affecting patient health condition.                     |
| `Alcohol_Use`           | Float (`float64`) | Numerical                   | Alcohol consumption level score of the patient.                                      |
| `Smoking`               | Float (`float64`) | Numerical                   | Smoking habit intensity/risk score.                                                  |
| `Obesity_Level`         | Float (`float64`) | Numerical                   | Obesity or body-fat-related risk score.                                              |
| `Cancer_Type`           | Object (String)   | Categorical                 | Type of cancer diagnosed (e.g., Lung, Breast, Skin, Leukemia, Colon).                |
| `Cancer_Stage`          | Object (String)   | Categorical                 | Stage of cancer progression (Stage 0, I, II, III, IV).                               |
| `Treatment_Cost_USD`    | Float (`float64`) | Numerical                   | Estimated treatment expenditure in US Dollars.                                       |
| `Survival_Years`        | Float (`float64`) | Numerical                   | Estimated survival duration after diagnosis in years.                                |
| `Target_Severity_Score` | Float (`float64`) | Numerical (Target Variable) | Overall severity score representing cancer risk intensity and condition seriousness. |

